	  If unsure select "N".

config SND_SOC_MT8133_M1
	tristate "ASoC Audio driver for MT8133 M1 Board"
	depends on SND_SOC_MT8168
	help
	  This adds support for ASoC machine driver for Mediatek MT8133
	  that used MT6357 codec.
	  Select Y if you have such device.
	  If unsure select "N".
	  Ex: MT8133

